.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, mystery, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, folk, jazz
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8
 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku   | skydiving | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | mystery  | western   | drama      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues    | folk      | jazz       |
| Sport         | sailing    | climbing | surfing   | cycling    |

